release_notes:
This update is recommended for all customers and includes an important reliability fix.
 
## Notable updates
- Fixed issue where client could take up to 1-2 minutes to recover connectivity instead of 1-2 seconds in the event of a service issue  
 
## Known issues
- No known issues
 
For Zero Trust documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-devices/warp
For Consumer documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/warp-client/
